text: Captain of the Black Guard is the longest-serving member of Malekith's personal army.
A member of the dark convents of the Sorceresses and serves the Witch King. She also commands wide range of destructive magic.
A High Mage of Saphery, a Princess, and a relative of the Phoenix King Finubar. she has led's the defense of Ulthuan againest the darkness that threat it.
As Chief Handmaiden it her sworn duty to protect the everqueen and lead her handmaidens into battle.
Lady Draya the Nighthawk is the ruler of High realm of Cythral.
